{"tid":1999943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛專家指死細胞或令檢測再呈陽性 實際上肺部已康復","createTime":"2020-05-03T13:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T17:26:02.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"20014e756782e712e5eb779e2dccbddc64941773","tid":1999943,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T13:41:02.000Z","msg":"世衛專家指死細胞或令檢測再呈陽性 實際上肺部已康復<br />\n2020-05-03 HKT 21:01<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織抗擊新型冠狀病毒小組一名專家指出，部分患者康復後，病毒檢測再呈陽性，可能並非再受感染，而是一些已死亡的細胞，令檢測呈陽性，實際上肺部已康復。<br />\n<br />\n不過該名專家強調，科學家仍在了解感染過病毒的人，康復後有幾大程度的免疫力。<br />\n<br />\n至於病毒源頭，她指蝙蝠是新型冠狀病毒的「天然源頭」，但暫時未能確定在蝙蝠及人類之間，有甚麼動物作為媒介，將病毒傳給人類。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1524029-20200503.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1524029-20200503.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgkpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=5a7cfeb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1524029-20200503.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=feb3159c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1524029-20200503.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"1e1c45d853e7372e8995b7e4706d191d73ee7d62","tid":1999943,"uid":264245,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T13:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁呢d死細胞有無傳染性先"},{"pid":"0bad94b729275be8855ebe1724231f7fd8eb4a0a","tid":1999943,"uid":279981,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T13:50:46.000Z","msg":"一名專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁威點解唔出真名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fb0b4a582f32b8442386a30834dc2ba6a99626","tid":1999943,"uid":16109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T13:53:04.000Z","msg":"WHO trust<img src=\"/a